  "planContent": "# 🏗️ Architecture Blueprint\n\n## App Overview\nA high-fidelity video viewing portal replicating the \"Kinetic Editorial\" aesthetic. The application provides a focused, immersive video consumption experience, complete with an interactive video player, metadata display, social engagement controls, and a dynamic sidebar for discovery, optimized for both desktop and mobile platforms.\n\n## Core Features\n- **Video Player**: Centralized interactive player with progress tracking, playback controls (play/pause, skip, volume, settings, fullscreen), and overlay gradients.\n- **Content Metadata**: Displays title, channel info, subscriber count, view counts, and timestamps.\n- **User Engagement**: Actionable buttons for Subscribe (toggle state), Like/Dislike (segmented control), Share, and Save (Download).\n- **Comment System**: Interactive input field for adding comments and a scrollable list of rendered user comments with like/reply capabilities.\n- **Sidebar Navigation**: \"Up Next\" list with category chips, autoplay toggle, and thumbnail-based video recommendations.\n- **Responsive Navigation**: Desktop top-bar with search/profile and mobile-optimized bottom navigation drawer.\n\n## UI & Layout Strategy\n- **Layout type**: Two-column responsive grid (main content + sidebar).\n- **Header**: Fixed top app bar containing the \"Kinetic Editorial\" wordmark, search trigger, and profile avatar.\n- **Main content area**: Left column hosts the video player and detailed metadata; right column hosts the \"Up Next\" list.\n- **Controls**: Primary action buttons (subscribe, like, share) using rounded-full pills; player controls integrated into a gradient overlay.\n- **Footer**: Mobile-only bottom navigation bar with icons for Home, Shorts, Subscriptions, and Library.\n- **Design System**: Tailwind CSS (Primary: #bc0100, Surface: #f9f9f9, Surface-Container: #e2e2e2).\n- **Color scheme**: Kinetic Editorial palette (Red/Surface/Zinc).\n- **Responsive strategy**: Stacked single-column on mobile (content first, then sidebar); side-by-side grid (1400px breakpoint).\n- **Animations & UX**: Tailwind transitions on hover (scale-105, bg-color changes).\n- **Touch Targets**: 44px min-height for all nav icons and primary CTA buttons.\n- **Accessibility**: Use `aria-label` for all icon-only buttons, maintain focus rings (`focus:ring-2`), and ensure high contrast text against backgrounds.\n\n## Data Model & State\n| Variable | Type | Default | Description |\n|----------|------|---------|-------------|\n| isPlaying | Boolean | false | Controls play/pause state |\n| currentTime | Number | 0 | Current video timestamp |\n| isSubscribed | Boolean | false | Channel subscription toggle |\n| comments | Array | [] | Collection of comment objects |\n| activeTab | String | 'All' | Selected chip in the sidebar |\n| likes | Number | 128000 | Like count |\n\n- **Persistence Strategy**: Use `window.forge.db.set('video_state', 'metadata', { isSubscribed, likes })`.\n\n## Technical Stack & Libraries\n- **Required CDNs**: Tailwind CSS (CDN), Material Symbols Outlined (Google Fonts), Inter Font (Google Fonts).\n- **Allowed**: Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons (as fallback/supplemental).\n- **APIs**: None (Static assets and mock data).\n\n## Implementation Steps\n1. Initialize the HTML shell with the provided Meta tags and Tailwind CDN configuration.\n2. Build the Fixed Header component and the Mobile Bottom Navigation component.\n3. Construct the Main Grid container (Desktop `lg:flex` layout).\n4. Implement the Video Player container with absolute positioning for the progress bar and controls.\n5. Create the Video Information metadata section (Title, Channel, Buttons).\n6. Build the Comment Section layout (Input bar and dynamic list).\n7. Implement the Sidebar (Up Next) with fixed-width constraints and overflow control.\n8. Add interactivity (Toggle `isPlaying`, `isSubscribed`, and like/comment state) using Vanilla JS.\n9. Verify responsive stacking behavior: move sidebar to bottom on screens < 1024px.\n10. Finalize touch targets and hover states for all primary interactive elements.\n\n## Edge Cases & Error Handling\n- **Empty State**: Show placeholder imagery/text if comments or recommendations fail to load.\n- **Overflow**: Ensure long video titles use `line-clamp-2`.\n- **Loading**: Use aspect-ratio containers (`aspect-video`) to prevent content layout shift during thumbnail loading.\n- **Validation**: Ensure comment inputs are trimmed of whitespace before updating the state array.",
  "currentHTML": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">\n    <title>The Kinetic Editorial - For You</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lucide@latest/dist/umd/lucide.min.js\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <script src=\"/forge.js\"></script>\n    <script>\n        tailwind.config = {\n            theme: {\n                extend: {\n                    colors: {\n                        primary: \"#bc0100\",\n                        \"on-primary\": \"#ffffff\",\n                        \"surface\": \"#f9f9f9\",\n                        \"on-surface\": \"#1a1c1c\",\n                        \"secondary\": \"#5f5e5e\",\n                        \"surface-container\": \"#eeeeee\",\n                        \"surface-container-highest\": \"#e2e2e2\",\n                        \"surface-container-low\": \"#f3f3f3\"\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }\n        .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n        .hide-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }\n        .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-surface text-on-surface\">\n\n<header class=\"fixed top-0 w-full flex justify-between items-center px-6 py-3 bg-surface/70 backdrop-blur-xl z-50\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl\">play_circle</span>\n        <h1 class=\"text-primary font-black tracking-tighter text-xl\">The Kinetic Editorial</h1>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\">\n        <button class=\"hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors p-2 rounded-full active:scale-95\">\n            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-zinc-500\">search</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-highest\">\n            <img referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAWmbwotQEyEhPwwTzosotTIADBw7tN_Y6_fVc0h-rfcKKc8TkJ57vgM-bsdTnNCr8AnX-m_5OD-ti38Tc-ynRn0uE0WGDbocQ1V8ANfx41MX1YwSQKbJB4qkofus5CgfX4nfbSFx9IWU5F1M3cVihC4K_nE-u7je9ckemlzJje9U2DxKrN0MjVC6p8_wB_6TKWENpSCtd40GcxUHd1m05P5iX50ik8R5-4q0EXGLrAVx_MfB4YpXkqUWLOY2LlpiWB0eNKeJoEIPE\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"pt-20 pb-24 px-4 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n    <section id=\"chipsContainer\" class=\"flex gap-3 overflow-x-auto hide-scrollbar mb-10 pb-2\"></section>\n\n    <section id=\"featuredSection\" class=\"mb-12\"></section>\n\n    <section class=\"mb-12\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">video_library</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black tracking-tight uppercase\">Shorts</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"shortsGrid\" class=\"flex gap-4 overflow-x-auto hide-scrollbar pb-4 -mx-4 px-4\"></div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"videosGrid\" class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"></section>\n</main>\n\n<nav class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-around items-center pt-3 pb-6 px-4 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-2xl rounded-t-3xl shadow-[0_-4px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]\">\n    <a class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold scale-110 transition-transform\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined mb-1\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">home</span>\n        <span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest\">Home</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-zinc-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined mb-1\">video_library</span>\n        <span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest\">Shorts</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-zinc-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined mb-1\">subscriptions</span>\n        <span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest\">Subs</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-zinc-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined mb-1\">video_settings</span>\n        <span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest\">Library</span>\n    </a>\n</nav>\n\n<script>\n    const data = {\n        chips: [\"All\", \"Digital Art\", \"Cinematography\", \"Motion Design\", \"Minimalism\", \"Editorial\"],\n        featured: {\n            title: \"Mastering the Art of Digital Curation: A New Era of Design\",\n            views: \"428K views\",\n            ago: \"2 hours ago\",\n            thumb: \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDxMtIIcRtczGdWyrDHeI6xfgrDdImc-iZNaTGBTmyz2sCWTxsCeJhYACAVWio11AvFWvhYfcgHHnVvLCDBForgFdravHE018MfvPpJY5Zbtjx3p4hvYAWp1qCTNBYnsEe6-QZKfG6B7h5-gzCb1ySIcniaay6M-wDc5Egni-okTFe44BLKbJkRX7BAgs9A0-S5l3DkFjmbAfL7rV_witXOzoLwjIcaJbDVJ2-I9lsoe74fEEZP0qvaXVCrm5SE7yVSd8Vm3VZ-Kyk\",\n            author: \"Curator Collective\"\n        },\n        shorts: [\n            { title: \"How to light your workspace\", views: \"1.2M\", img: \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBT4va2rnj2FRVvXYf2IKRYTIyiPHqBPMBLw8j8eNjoZ0o8i5h73v13va7jbc4ce9CPqXqzBLDbYo44bFhpT3u6MWl83FMCxw0M5YrjwMsrRQRZmWJtPKbhkIq7UJ-dmTxljc1geo5QK7tzj2qmfZ7-wgQM_f4vbpoHo1eZhMdHBZeFs_Tfb-pZz923YS96ep7DTujo_SWPHJ310N1abw1fIPqvc-lzcQZYC1uryQFUBEAf4PTW1VszZqcgqDMN0shw9bnmwx4sXgI\" },\n            { title: \"Generative Typography\", views: \"856K\", img: \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuACb4Zg43TBzUbHEThqmTeGr_z2LGkNCAs2ujAD34Vv08UUvTLIH0M7UOHLvLTAwsLXtgwP0-05YaR7MvM0IC4152q9UHsPIYoMY8u6LeHep33bRnWD_L_CAzH7Tjo2it-B5QsbelsmMw-y-bJcRHvIgTm-LWX5w2RxWWRpR4qUfAj0v2jdRVXPtPVcgW7mT4FPsyhUWuvrI4x5P_R9efIAFBVrxRDPXA10ylaf0TbZ8Zfwxarqpuuq6KdigLub169rUl1CS8jLvZY\" }\n        ],\n        videos: [\n            { title: \"Cinematic Landscapes: Lighting and Mood\", views: \"1.5M\", author: \"Visionary Films\", img: \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAOGEHqLoJZd5nIuKHCvfF8lBtt5V_chC8LYBLhJr7CiimoNH_OeQPFs8g-63YxmzkTOVjbWcPNFcthgEOEDcCq6maEYcHsRqF6YqwJmlKfve346ROT5LaBZf5G9PlOGklIPmW2PiKU9bKnttohvFO31oMguHc1IILIdkzkDxd2w9oWws6ECUIxlRB7R1aepykVGQN_SlIJkMUof4tVEgCppcFvxzH7rAGJ9zWOTGF6a9JVdbY5DXEBfzk5LK9z42VolXVVqkNX-TM\" },\n            { title: \"Minimalism as a Strategy\", views: \"289K\", author: \"Design Systems Inc.\", img: \"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAGJ0Ao-_nTmkXpyInDfCDKbDDw_4kEV-wwo5kOxtImLZrmrjHLO_NhZxTBhOk0Pj_TxVtG4npeQWyYwa7lu3MmSho1xzqMH-3TGU2mG-z5sIRHSlbTFDVk78Kj1AEqX1Gsxu1qql9fjiXi-8KZoyOChyk24ty6HPiqJS_L1utUOnma4UjH1HkjLcQWBD05UcN2BAJHGydx4TI5uSLQXNxROEjHths--5KFQ7b0bcK5Fpgxe2aGRy_XNxJHx0u2ehZtppPWZU_URc0\" }\n        ]\n    };\n\n    async function init() {\n        document.getElementById('chipsContainer').innerHTML = data.chips.map((c, i) => `\n            <button class=\"px-5 py-2 ${i === 0 ? 'bg-on-surface text-on-primary' : 'bg-surface-container-highest'} rounded-full text-sm font-bold whitespace-nowrap\">\n                ${c}\n            </button>`).join('');\n\n        document.getElementById('featuredSection').innerHTML = `\n            <div class=\"relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-container-lowest\">\n                <div class=\"aspect-video w-full overflow-hidden\">\n                    <img referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" src=\"${data.featured.thumb}\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 flex gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"space-y-1\">\n                        <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">${data.featured.title}</h2>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-secondary text-sm\">\n                            <span class=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">${data.featured.author}</span>\n                            <span>• ${data.featured.views}</span>\n                            <span>• ${data.featured.ago}</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>`;\n\n        document.getElementById('shortsGrid').innerHTML = data.shorts.map(s => `\n            <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-44 md:w-56 group cursor-pointer\">\n                <div class=\"aspect-[9/16] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-3 relative\">\n                    <img referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" src=\"${s.img}\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-3 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent\">\n                        <p class=\"text-white text-sm font-bold\">${s.title}</p>\n                        <p class=\"text-white/70 text-[10px]\">${s.views} views</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>`).join('');\n\n        document.getElementById('videosGrid').innerHTML = data.videos.map(v => `\n            <div class=\"group cursor-pointer\">\n                <div class=\"aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-surface-container relative mb-4\">\n                    <img referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" src=\"${v.img}\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-md leading-tight mb-1\">${v.title}</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-secondary text-xs\">${v.author} • ${v.views} views</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>`).join('');\n    }\n\n    init();\n</script>\n<footer class=\"text-center p-4 text-neutral-400 text-xs opacity-80 flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5 mt-auto\"><span>Built with</span> <img src=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app/logo.png\" alt=\"Forge\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-sm object-cover\"> <a href=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app\" class=\"text-blue-500 font-semibold tracking-wide no-underline\">FORGE</a></footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
